<h2 id="dubbo-admin监控管理" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#dubbo-admin监控管理" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Dubbo admin监控管理</h2>
<p>sudo docker run -d  -p 2181:2181 --name zookeeper zookeeper</p>
<p>docker run -p  8080:8080  -d  -e   admin.registry.address=zookeeper://zookeeper:2181   -e  admin.config-center=zookeeper://zookeeper:2181     -e  admin.metadata-report.address=zookeeper://zookeeper:2181   --link  zookeeper:zookeeper  --name dubbo    apache/dubbo-admin</p>
